  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA385">
<l>            ellai ceṉṟapiṉ malaruṅ kūmpiṉa</l>
<l>            pulavunī raṭaikarai yāmai pārppō</l>
<l>            ṭalavaṉu maḷaivayiṟ ceṟintaṉa koṭuṅkaḻi</l>
<l>            yirainacai varuttam vīṭa maramicaip</l>
<l>            puḷḷum piḷḷaiyoṭu vatintaṉa vataṉāṟ</l>
<l>            poḻutaṉ ṟātaliṟ ṟamiyai varuti</l>
<l>            yeḻuteḻiṉ maḻaikka[ṇ]</l>
            </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent">            After the daylight is gone</l>
<l rend="indent4">            the blossoms have closed,</l>
<l>        and the crabs have come to keep to [their] holes with</l>
<l rend="indent">         the young ones of the tortoise on the settling shore of the fish-reeking water,</l>
<l>        and the birds have come to stay with [their] young ones on the trees</l>
<l rend="indent">         to destroy their yearning suffering for prey from the curved backwaters.</l>
<l rend="indent4">            Therefore,</l>
<l>        since this is not the time,</l>
<l rend="indent4">            you would come solitary,</l>
<l>        o you of rain eyes with [collyrium-]drawn grace ...</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
